<br>
Draw a line between hermit hut and SW to a little hill with an aviak perch on it.  Kill everything you can see within visable range while traveling between these 2 points.<br>
<br>
Draw a line from Shadowman camp to PAW, everything you can see within visable range while traveling between these 2 points.<br>
<br>
By doing 1 of these 2 areas, over and over again, I have managed to see and kill Quillmane.  However, it has always been legs.  Concentrating on &quot;named&quot; spawns is good to do, but I normally just kill everything in sight.  60 water pet with velocity and buffs does the job pretty well.<br>
<br>
If you do have to make a choice though, kill the named types before you bother with lions and such.<br>
